  "pages": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "This multi-block structure cannot be formed with a single block. $(br2) It is a structure that adds star levels to the $(6) Energy Condenser $() by using materials. $(br2) There are two modes for this structure: increasing the maximum star count and increasing the star count. $(br2) The star count mode can only be used when the maximum star count is present. "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "There are four levels for this structure, and the corresponding bases are: Wood Pedestal, Pedestal, Dark Matter Pedestal, and Star Injector. $(br2) All recipes can be found in JEI. $(br2) For the same type of base, the placement of items above it is unordered. $(br2) After placing the materials, put the $(6) Energy Condenser $() on top of the core, right-click with a Resonant Star Wand, and wait for the synthesis to complete. $(br2) After the synthesis is completed, the items on the pedestal will be consumed, and the corresponding effect will be achieved. "
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "It should be noted that different recipes may correspond to different constellations, in which case you need to adjust the corresponding star of the focusing crystal above. $(br2) For the $(6) Energy Condenser $(), each star will increase its omnidirectional panel by 1%, the second star by 2%, the third by 3%, and so on. $(br2) $(c)Currently$() each synthesis only takes 3 seconds and has a 100% success rate. $(br2) After building the multi-block structure, the focusing crystal above it will emit light of different colors. See the next page for the multi-block structure. "
    },
